Concept of ORCHESTRATION

What is the orchestration?
ans) In simple terms, orchestration is the automation of process across 
muitiple systems to ensure that the right tasks happen in the right order
with minimum manual intervention.

Key goals of orchestration
. Automation of workflows (eg: CI/CD pipelines)
. Environment provisioning (eg: spin up serevrs or containers)
. Configuration management
. Service Deployment
. Resource management across cloud, on-prem, or hybrid infrastructures
. Monitoring and alerting.

Benefits of Orchestration in Devops
--> Faster and reliable deployments.
--> Reduced manual errors.
--> Scalability of infrastucture and services.
--> Improved visibility and monitoring.
--> Consistency across environment.